{
  "stem": "8359.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was, I think, about a week or two weeks before the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What did the leaflet say?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was addressed to the German people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember-- I wish I had held onto one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wish that I had held onto one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You killed enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stop your killing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't bring back the ones you killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stop your killing now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you are really going to suffer consequences and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was signed Roosevelt, Stalin, and Churchill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's when we knew that-- oh, how I wish I had-- but you know, who thinks, you know, at a time like this?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you felt the end was coming near?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, I think, about a week later-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] get up one morning, and we don't see any SS women-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this man, this Vuichu, the German soldiers were retreating with their guns and whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were, by that time, I would say, at least 2,000 girls in that camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they brought in a huge amount of the Hungarian in 1944, end of 1944 when Eichmann came into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And funny thing is, I think they brought him into us from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they came with their hair shaved off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, we always had our hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it wasn't always clean, believe me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were all young women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were afraid to be there alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like I said, they-- no civilian had any jurisdiction over us as long as the Nazis, the SS, was in control.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About three days.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Without anyone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he got a couple of his friends, and they had guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stood at the gate of our camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they guarded us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How about food?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
